!!! info "Data Source"
    Every Cabrillo log file contains a `CREATED-BY:` header identifying the logging software.
    We parse these headers from 496K+ logs downloaded from CQ and ARRL contest results.
    No operator identifiers are stored — this is aggregate statistics only.

