## Platform Gap

The contest logging market is **100% Windows** at the top. macOS options
(SkookumLogger, RUMlogNG, MacLoggerDX) and Linux options (TLF, CQRLOG, YFKtest)
together represent less than 1% of submissions.

This isn't a sample bias — it's the entire population of submitted Cabrillo logs
from 15 major contests over 20 years.

For more on how this data was collected, see the
[methodology page](../methodology/index.md).

